name: Cats vs Cucumbers
description:
According to reports provided by the internet, cats have been embarrassed when it comes to facing cucumbers.

Now it's time for revenge, this game is about cats coming together to defeat cucumbers!

Made in under 72 hours for Clicker Jam 2 (Theme: "Green").

Artist - Letícia Yasmin (@leticiayas182)

Programmer - Raul Pavani (@raulpavani)
